info.name: Akazawa Izumi - Roblox Theme
info.description: This is the fixed version of the original, which is now properly titled and working. Low Quality Warning: This is the best I can do, as I got it straight from the source, if you found a 1024p version please give me an imgur link to it or type out the link but don't put a dot in between it. All credits go to the horror anime, >Another<, for the gif, the girl is Akazawa Izumi. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads, or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. The original theme was this falsely titled Yumeko Jabami. It's a link. 31 October 2022 - Released. 1 July 2023 - Revamped style with new base code.
